1.title: The F.N.G.
1.plot: Just another day for Lee and Cal as they portray cartoon characters Ally-Gator and Skunk-Rat. Today, they meet the guy playing the new Jackass of the park and try to give him some quick lessons about what it means to be a character.

2.title: Fu**Ing Face Actors
2.plot: There's a civil war raging inside of Cosmic Adventures Theme Park between two factions: The lovable costumed characters and the dick-wad Face Actors. The princess is also crazy AF.

imdb.plot outline: With these characters, it's not who they are on the outside, but who's portraying them inside. Lee and Cal play Ally-Gator and Skunk-Rat, respectively, but they don't necessarily show any respect for the job. They talk while in costume, hit on girls, sell drugs only to hit on the hot princess in the park and pick fights with the face actors. One thing's for sure, they definitely don't make the job boring.
imdb.title: Characters
plot: If you stay in town after high school, working at Cosmic Adventures theme park isn't the only option, it's the worst option.::Chris Naylor
